(*****************************************************************************
 *                           COMPILATION                                     *
 *          = ELABORATION + TRANSLATION TO FLINT + CODE GENERATION           *
 * used by interact/evalloop.sml, batch/batchutil.sml, batch/cmsa.sml only   * 
